				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<p class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">
<p>Sanskar Radio's motto is to promote Sanatana Hindu Dharma involves actively spreading its principles, teachings, and practices, often through teaching, living an exemplary life, and engaging in community activities. This can include sharing knowledge about dharma, its values, and its practical application in daily life via broadcasting religious, social and cultural programs.</p>
<p> We broadcast programs on DAB Radio and on line Sanskarradio.com during whole year from 7 am to 9pm followed by back-to-back devotional music. We also celebrate all Sanatan Hindu Festivals throughout the year. Our presenters are serving the whole community voluntarily.</p></p>				</div>
