				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2852984 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="2852984" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<p class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">
<p>Sri Prem Khosla, a cherished voice and guiding light of our stations. Khosla ji was not only a respected leader but also a beloved presenter who brought warmth, wisdom, and dedication to the airwaves.</p>
<p>He played a pivotal role in the launch of Sabras Radio in the mid-1990s and Sanskar Radio in 2004 and remained a vital part of its journey. Listeners across generations connected with his sincere voice and spiritual presence on Sanskar Radio.</p>
<p>His legacy continues to inspire all who knew him and heard him. We honour his contributions and deeply miss his presence. His blessings are with us, and we keep the legacy he created to serve our community in better ways.</p></p>				</div>
